    <h2>3. In-App Purchases / Tips</h2>
    <p>
      The App <strong>does not</strong> offer optional in-app purchases or tips.
    </p>
    <p>
      The App does not collect or store any payment or billing information.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>
      The App does not sell, trade, or rent user data to third parties.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>
